H0.text: What is a Teeter-Totter more commonly called. Seesaw

H1.text: What is a Teeter-Totter more commonly called. Dandle

H2.text: What is a Teeter-Totter more commonly called. Tilting Board

H3.text: What is a Teeter-Totter more commonly called. C-saw

A4.text: A teeter-totter is also referred to as a seesaw.

A5.text: In the southeastern New England region of the United States, it is sometimes referred to as a tilt or a tilting board.
